                <p>To apply for a job at Delta Airlines, you should visit their official careers page at delta.com/careers. From there, you can browse available job listings by category, such as flight attendants, pilots, customer support, and more. Once you find a position that matches your skills and qualifications, you can submit your application online, upload relevant documents, and include links to your professional social media profiles.</p>
